background_description: The scene depicts expansive sand dunes with undulating ridges and valleys. The sand is light beige to golden brown, showing fine wind-blown ripples and patterns. Tufts of vibrant green dune grass grow in clusters on the dunes and along their crests. The sky above is largely covered with an overcast layer of white and grey stratocumulus clouds, with some hints of lighter blue sky peeking through.
